Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.15,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(452,154)\fad(0,300)}{\3c&HFF00FF&}{\bord2}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.74,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,245,-100,245)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HEFEFEF&}{\bord3}要取下对方的棋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.15,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,420)\fad(0,300)}{\3c&HFF0000&}{\bord2}优希
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.62,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0600,0100)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HEFEFEF&}{\bord2}{\pos(320,388)}{\fs20}在围棋中 规定只要把对方的棋子围起来 就可以取下对方的棋子
